      <title>腐败丑闻给哥伦比亚财政部长带来更多压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/corruption-scandal-adds-to-pressure-on-colombia-s-finance-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚财政部长因涉嫌腐败丑闻而受到新的指控，在政府试图应对日益加深的财政危机之际，这给总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗带来了更多麻烦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/corruption-scandal-adds-to-pressure-on-colombia-s-finance-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 18:24:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
