      <title>Jane Street 称前交易员嘲笑“愚蠢”的千禧年策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/jane-street-says-ex-trader-mocked-dumb-millennium-strategies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[简街集团 (Jane Street Group) 称，一名前交易员曾嘲笑其新雇主的策略“愚蠢”，该交易员声称此人为千禧年管理公司 (Millennium Management) 窃取了价值数十亿美元的印度期权秘密策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/jane-street-says-ex-trader-mocked-dumb-millennium-strategies</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 18:07:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
