    <item>
      <title>芝加哥计划在预算僵局中再融资 8.06 亿美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/chicago-plans-806-million-bond-refinancing-amid-budget-standoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥市长布兰登·约翰逊 (Brandon Johnson) 正努力在年底前弥补近 10 亿美元的预算缺口，作为再融资的一部分，芝加哥计划本周发售约 8.06 亿美元的市政债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/chicago-plans-806-million-bond-refinancing-amid-budget-standoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 17:45:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Prime Capital 收购 RES 的瑞典绿色航空燃料项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/prime-capital-buys-swedish-green-aviation-fuel-project-from-res</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国资产管理公司 Prime Capital AG 收购了瑞典的一个合成航空燃料项目，此举将推动该国在近期遭遇挫折后推动绿色技术转型。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/prime-capital-buys-swedish-green-aviation-fuel-project-from-res</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将宣布向乌克兰提供价值 7.25 亿美元的新武器计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/us-to-announce-725-million-arms-package-for-ukraine-including-mines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据两名官员透露，美国即将宣布向乌克兰提供最新一批武器，这些武器均来自美国库存，总额约为 7.25 亿美元，其中包括总统乔·拜登批准的第二批杀伤人员地雷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/us-to-announce-725-million-arms-package-for-ukraine-including-mines</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 16:24:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃莱克特拉股价暴跌，萨利纳斯一天将损失 40 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/salinas-set-to-lose-4-billion-in-a-day-as-elektra-slumps-60</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在监管机构下令交易所在停牌数月后恢复交易后，Grupo Elektra 股价周一暴跌逾 60%，亿万富翁里卡多·萨利纳斯·普利戈 (Ricardo Salinas Pliego) 的财富因此蒸发约 40 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/salinas-set-to-lose-4-billion-in-a-day-as-elektra-slumps-60</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 15:43:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
